## JWE Encrypt Decrypt Integration Custom Credentials:

The JWE Encrypt and Decrypt examples expect some custom credentials at the Genesys Function Data Actions integration level:
* PUBLIC_KEY: Public Key to perform the JWE Encryption
* PRIVATE_KEY: Private Key to perform the JWE Decryption
